{
  "id": "adv_event_2306_01_05",
  "title": "想いは\n変わらない",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――スペシャルライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of special live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.9800000668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ始まるんだね\n私達のスペシャルライブ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Finally‚ it's starting.\nOur special live…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7333333175,
      "endTime": 7.5179367225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "いつものライブとはまた違う緊張感があるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a different tension compared to usual lives.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7333333175,
      "endTime": 12.2466669242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.4496147712
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "私達にやれることは全部やったわ\n後はステージで全力を尽くすだけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've done everything we can.\nAll that's left is to give it our all on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4496147712,
      "endTime": 18.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "大袈裟ね。観客は身内だけなんだから\nそんなに気を張らなくていいでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're exaggerating. Since the audience is just our people‚\nyou don't need to be so tense.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.582175541,
      "endTime": 24.986143684399998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.182175541
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "それは違います。相手が身内だからこそ\n余計に手を抜く訳にはいかないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ that's not true. Because they're family‚\nwe can't afford to slack off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.182175541,
      "endTime": 31.8430363655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.0459842126
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "初めて会った時からどれだけ成長したか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've come so far since we first met…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0459842126,
      "endTime": 35.841292850399995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "今の私達の全力のパフォーマンスを観てもらうことが\n感謝の気持ちを表すことになるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our current performance is a way\nto express our gratitude.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0442406974,
      "endTime": 42.104578050200004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.3075258973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "手を抜いたライブでは想いは伝わらない\nだから私達は万全の準備をしてきたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Feelings won't be conveyed with a half-hearted performance.\nThat's why we've prepared thoroughly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3075258973,
      "endTime": 48.4507706246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.6408561788
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "それとも、スリクスは手を抜くつもりだったのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Or did IIIX plan to slack off?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6408561788,
      "endTime": 52.507527947599996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳ないでしょ。スリクスはどんなライブでも\n最高のパフォーマンスをするだけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no way that's true.\nIIIX always gives their best in any performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6741930726,
      "endTime": 59.3408598664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.5408597393
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "……いいわ、今日は{user}さんに\nどのグループが一番優れているか見せつけてあげる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Fine‚ today I'll show {user}-san\nwhich group is the most outstanding.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5408597393,
      "endTime": 67.3671410961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.5741930726
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよね！　{user}さんには\n最高の私達を見てほしいですよね！　分かります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! We want {user}-san to see us\nat our best‚ don't you? I see!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.5741930726,
      "endTime": 74.5552815202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.7408597393
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで最高のパフォーマンスをして\nみんなで一番になりましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's give the best performance together and\naim to be the best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7408597393,
      "endTime": 79.621925394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.8075264059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……挑発したつもりなんだけど……\nそういえばkanaもさくらは面白いとか言ってたっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh… I thought I was provoking them…\nCome to think of it‚ didn't kana also find Sakura fun?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8075264059,
      "endTime": 89.7075267873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "…………あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "………… Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2333333333,
      "endTime": 92.8741961402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.5408755066
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん？　どうかしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san? What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5408755066,
      "endTime": 96.3108769657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.7804950399
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい。この顔ぶれでこんな風に\n言い合える日が来るなんて、なんだか感慨深くて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry. Seeing this group and how far we've come…\nIt's just so… nostalgic and moving…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.7804950399,
      "endTime": 104.2314020796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.4471617065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "私と麻奈ちゃんの二人しかいなかった頃は\nこんな光景、想像も出来なかったわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When it was just Mana-chan and me‚\nI couldn't imagine such a scene…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.4471617065,
      "endTime": 110.76160605769999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.9471617065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "しんみりしないで下さい\n満足するのはまだ早いですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't get sentimental.\nIt's too early to be satisfied.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.9471617065,
      "endTime": 115.4604976973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.6634455444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ここがゴールじゃないでしょ\n星見プロはこれからも続いていくんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This isn't the end.\nHoshimi Prods will continue to exist.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.6634455444,
      "endTime": 120.6634267411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.9634409667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "ⅢXがいるのに、いつまでもうだつの上がらない\n零細事務所じゃ困るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even with IIIX around‚\nwe can't stay as a small agency forever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9634409667,
      "endTime": 126.5202211142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.7301076334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんと遙子さんの二人で始まって\nサニピと月ストが誕生して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Starting with you and Haruko-san‚\nthen Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.7301076334,
      "endTime": 132.5178643625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルとリズノワ、それにスリクスが加わって\n星見プロはこれからもっと輝きを増していくんだよ",
      "translations": {
